data.description: Fabulous & very unique home on huge lot with in ground pool. 12' ceiling in family/dining room, updated carpet, light fixtures, paint, kitchen counter tops & appliances. French doors to 3rd BR. Wonderful sun room w/french doors to covered patio w/surround sound and extra deck overlooking pool. New H/A & roof 2009, sprinkler system 2003, new pool liner 2010, pump & cover 2013. Huge corner lot in cul-de-sac w/side load garage, 2 storage bldgs, extensive landscaping. A must see property. Some exclusions. Brokered And Advertised By: Gloria Rand Realty, Inc. Listing Agent: Linda Peterson
